text: Erika Fairweather is a swimmer from New Zealand. Fairweather competed at the 2019 World Aquatics Championships and the 2020 Summer Olympics. She was born on 31 December 2003.Erika Fairweather == References == Category:2003 births Category:Living people Category:New Zealand swimmers Category:Olympians for New Zealand Category:Sportspeople from Dunedin
